cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on natural language processing tasks such as reading comprehension and question answering, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of attention networks and language embeddings suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of hierarchical attention networks suggests a focus on neural networks and deep learning, which are covered by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
